swing the gate
Homonym Number:
Word Class:phrase
Sense Number:
Definition:1. to be the fastest shearer in the shed. 2.  to draft stock for sale or act as 'picker'. 3. to hurry.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
